node.title: Police launch investigation into death of Gisborne toddler
node.description: Gisborne Police have launched a homicide investigation into the death of a 19-month-old toddler.
node.content:
["Gisborne Police have launched a homicide investigation into the death of a 19-month-old toddler.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Claire Eastham-Farrelly\n
", "The child was brought into Gisborne Hospital with critical injuries on Thursday 6 January.", "They were subsequently flown to Starship Hospital but died today.", "A police spokesperson said they were continuing to investigate the nature and circumstances surrounding the child's injuries.", "A scene examination has been completed at a residential address in the Gisborne suburb of Te Hapara."]
